5.4 Dependency Injection Strategy
Framework: Hilt (default) or Koin (justify if chosen)
Scope mapping: Singleton / ActivityRetained / ViewModel / Fragment
5.5 Async and Threading Strategy
Coroutines + Flow/StateFlow for all async work
Dispatcher mapping:
Dispatchers.IO for network and disk
Dispatchers.Default for CPU-intensive work
Dispatchers.Main for UI updates only
WorkManager for deferrable background tasks
5.6 Error Handling Strategy
Sealed Result wrapper: sealed class Result { data class Success(val data: T) data class Error(val exception: Throwable, val message: String) object Loading }

Every repository method returns Flow<Result>. ViewModels map to UiState. Never swallow exceptions silently.

